1
00:00:38,820 --> 00:00:40,820
=Visage and Soul=

2
00:00:40,820 --> 00:00:43,040
(The "Different Her"
Trilogy on Women's Relationships)

3
00:00:44,720 --> 00:00:47,640
=Episode 11=

4
00:00:49,440 --> 00:00:50,120
Xiaomi.

5
00:00:50,120 --> 00:00:52,200
These paintings we picked
out for the exhibition

6
00:00:52,200 --> 00:00:53,360
are absolutely incredible.

7
00:00:53,720 --> 00:00:54,640
Look at this one.

8
00:00:54,960 --> 00:00:56,560
The colors and composition

9
00:00:56,560 --> 00:00:57,560
are both bold and inspired.

10
00:00:57,560 --> 00:00:58,440
The sense of vitality

11
00:00:58,440 --> 00:01:00,080
is practically bursting off the canvas.

12
00:01:01,400 --> 00:01:02,800
Even though it doesn't quite match

13
00:01:02,800 --> 00:01:04,480
our gallery's usual style,

14
00:01:04,760 --> 00:01:06,800
this kind of breakthrough
is exactly what we need.

15
00:01:08,000 --> 00:01:08,880
And this one.

16
00:01:09,360 --> 00:01:11,680
The linework is so
delicate and expressive.

17
00:01:12,280 --> 00:01:13,400
This exhibition of ours

18
00:01:13,400 --> 00:01:14,880
is definitely going
to be a huge success.

19
00:01:17,240 --> 00:01:18,640
They are pretty amazing.

20
00:01:24,400 --> 00:01:26,200
Looks like this so-called business trip

21
00:01:26,200 --> 00:01:27,200
was actually pretty sweet.

22
00:01:27,880 --> 00:01:28,520
Come on, tell me.

23
00:01:28,520 --> 00:01:30,280
When are you planning to marry him?

24
00:01:31,680 --> 00:01:32,760
Marry?

25
00:01:32,920 --> 00:01:33,720
Yeah.

26
00:01:33,720 --> 00:01:35,240
Aren't you two planning to get married?

27
00:01:36,080 --> 00:01:38,280
I don't even know who I am yet.

28
00:01:38,880 --> 00:01:40,240
How could I possibly

29
00:01:40,240 --> 00:01:41,280
promise someone a lifetime?

30
00:01:42,000 --> 00:01:42,920
That's true.

31
00:01:42,920 --> 00:01:44,920
Marriage is a major life
decision, after all.

32
00:01:44,920 --> 00:01:45,640
No rush.

33
00:01:50,200 --> 00:01:50,720
Yifei.

34
00:01:52,000 --> 00:01:53,720
When HR hired you,

35
00:01:53,720 --> 00:01:54,800
did they know we knew each other?

36
00:01:55,400 --> 00:01:56,520
I never told them.

37
00:01:56,520 --> 00:01:58,320
I got this job on my own.

38
00:02:02,120 --> 00:02:03,120
I see.

39
00:02:19,080 --> 00:02:20,360
You've seemed pretty happy lately.

40
00:02:20,360 --> 00:02:21,800
Something making you happy?

41
00:02:24,080 --> 00:02:25,880
Qin Yu and I went on a trip together.

42
00:02:26,480 --> 00:02:28,200
That trip made me realize

43
00:02:29,160 --> 00:02:31,320
that maybe it wouldn't be so scary

44
00:02:31,800 --> 00:02:33,320
if those memories never came back.

45
00:02:37,320 --> 00:02:38,240
So,

46
00:02:39,000 --> 00:02:40,640
when you're with Qin Yu,

47
00:02:41,120 --> 00:02:42,400
he makes you feel secure?

48
00:02:46,400 --> 00:02:48,200
When I'm with him,

49
00:02:49,400 --> 00:02:51,280
I feel relaxed,

50
00:02:52,120 --> 00:02:53,120
and happy.

51
00:02:57,000 --> 00:02:57,840
How about this?

52
00:02:58,120 --> 00:02:59,400
Next time you come,

53
00:02:59,400 --> 00:03:00,280
bring him with you.

54
00:03:00,760 --> 00:03:02,160
That way I can get

55
00:03:02,160 --> 00:03:03,200
a better sense of how you're doing.

56
00:03:04,200 --> 00:03:05,560
Bring him too?

57
00:03:07,520 --> 00:03:08,760
Is that really necessary?

58
00:03:12,760 --> 00:03:13,600
Maybe

59
00:03:15,120 --> 00:03:16,640
I really should move on.

60
00:03:22,800 --> 00:03:24,080
Thank you, Dr. Chen.

61
00:03:24,280 --> 00:03:25,480
Qin Yu's waiting for
me to help him move.

62
00:03:25,480 --> 00:03:26,160
I'd better go.

63
00:03:44,000 --> 00:03:45,800
Why are you always so impulsive?

64
00:03:45,800 --> 00:03:47,000
Now all of a sudden you're moving.

65
00:03:48,760 --> 00:03:50,760
A hotel just doesn't feel like home.

66
00:03:51,280 --> 00:03:51,920
Think about it.

67
00:03:52,280 --> 00:03:53,480
If I'm going to teach you how to paint,

68
00:03:53,480 --> 00:03:55,560
We need a bright, spacious place.

69
00:03:56,520 --> 00:03:57,880
And if you end up
painting late into the night,

70
00:03:57,880 --> 00:03:59,640
you'll need somewhere
comfortable to eat and sleep.

71
00:03:59,640 --> 00:04:01,600
My house is already big enough.

72
00:04:02,600 --> 00:04:04,560
At the Qiao house, you've got
to watch out for Qiao Zhiwei.

73
00:04:04,880 --> 00:04:05,800
At the gallery,

74
00:04:06,120 --> 00:04:07,520
you have to act like the boss.

75
00:04:08,040 --> 00:04:08,880
But here,

76
00:04:09,440 --> 00:04:11,800
you can lose your temper
whenever you want.

77
00:04:16,320 --> 00:04:18,440
And while you're at it,
help out around the house.

78
00:04:18,440 --> 00:04:19,240
Laundry,

79
00:04:19,240 --> 00:04:20,920
cooking, mopping, washing dishes.

80
00:04:20,920 --> 00:04:22,680
You'll have all the freedom you want.

81
00:04:24,840 --> 00:04:26,800
Qin Yu, you've really
thought of everything.

82
00:05:10,480 --> 00:05:12,520
We'll be able to send
it out in a few days.

83
00:05:40,320 --> 00:05:41,240
What's this?

84
00:05:47,520 --> 00:05:48,600
I'm talking to you.

85
00:05:50,760 --> 00:05:51,760
What are you doing?

86
00:05:52,120 --> 00:05:53,440
What do you think I'm doing?

87
00:05:54,720 --> 00:05:55,840
Get away from me.

88
00:05:56,200 --> 00:05:57,080
Let go!

89
00:05:58,320 --> 00:05:59,560
You're so weird.

90
00:06:51,160 --> 00:06:52,200
It's so late.

91
00:06:52,200 --> 00:06:53,480
Why are you still here?

92
00:06:54,920 --> 00:06:55,800
What about you?

93
00:06:59,320 --> 00:06:59,960
Wait.

94
00:07:01,960 --> 00:07:02,920
What is it

95
00:07:03,480 --> 00:07:04,560
that you carry in that bag

96
00:07:04,760 --> 00:07:05,600
every day?

97
00:07:05,960 --> 00:07:07,080
It's nothing.

98
00:07:07,720 --> 00:07:09,200
Just some books.

99
00:07:10,280 --> 00:07:11,680
And...

100
00:07:12,240 --> 00:07:13,320
And what else?

101
00:07:19,600 --> 00:07:21,600
This is something
my mom and I made together.

102
00:07:23,760 --> 00:07:24,720
A pressed mugwort leaf.

103
00:07:26,480 --> 00:07:27,360
What's

104
00:07:27,600 --> 00:07:28,720
this for?

105
00:07:30,360 --> 00:07:31,920
My mom used to say,

106
00:07:31,920 --> 00:07:33,920
if you ever want to thank someone

107
00:07:33,920 --> 00:07:35,800
but don't know what to give them,

108
00:07:37,040 --> 00:07:38,520
give them a mugwort leaf.

109
00:07:39,840 --> 00:07:41,320
Because it's simple and pure.

110
00:07:41,800 --> 00:07:43,560
And its fragrance

111
00:07:43,880 --> 00:07:45,280
lingers for a very long time.

112
00:07:59,480 --> 00:08:00,720
I'll keep it nicely!

113
00:08:18,680 --> 00:08:19,800
What are you doing here?

114
00:08:20,240 --> 00:08:21,800
Of course I'm here to
pick you up for work.

115
00:08:21,800 --> 00:08:24,160
Today's exhibition means
something different to you.

116
00:08:24,840 --> 00:08:25,960
On such an important day,

117
00:08:25,960 --> 00:08:26,960
how could I possibly miss it?

118
00:08:28,600 --> 00:08:30,440
You have so little faith in me?

119
00:08:31,120 --> 00:08:32,680
This exhibition isn't just about you.

120
00:08:33,080 --> 00:08:35,040
It's also a chance
to prove I have great taste.

121
00:08:35,920 --> 00:08:37,040
I picked all the paintings.

122
00:08:37,760 --> 00:08:38,520
Whether we win

123
00:08:38,680 --> 00:08:39,480
or lose,

124
00:08:41,960 --> 00:08:42,600
from now on,

125
00:08:42,960 --> 00:08:44,560
we're in the same boat.

126
00:08:46,040 --> 00:08:47,560
Who says I'm in the same boat as you?

127
00:08:51,080 --> 00:08:52,560
Captain,

128
00:08:52,960 --> 00:08:54,240
cut me some slack.

129
00:08:58,920 --> 00:08:59,800
Alright then.

130
00:09:00,400 --> 00:09:01,800
Let's ride

131
00:09:02,480 --> 00:09:03,720
the waves together.

132
00:09:18,120 --> 00:09:18,800
Xiaomi.

133
00:09:18,800 --> 00:09:19,920
You're here.

134
00:09:19,920 --> 00:09:21,200
Everything's ready.

135
00:09:21,200 --> 00:09:22,600
We're just waiting for
your final approval.

136
00:09:23,600 --> 00:09:25,960
These works are definitely going
to get an amazing response.

137
00:09:25,960 --> 00:09:27,880
Everyone's been waiting
to see your father's final work.

138
00:09:29,240 --> 00:09:30,720
This painting is beautiful.

139
00:09:32,160 --> 00:09:33,280
The title is beautiful too.

140
00:09:34,320 --> 00:09:35,400
Love That Remains.

141
00:09:47,560 --> 00:09:48,280
What's wrong?

142
00:09:50,280 --> 00:09:50,960
Nothing.

143
00:09:55,840 --> 00:09:56,600
Qin Yu.

144
00:09:57,160 --> 00:09:58,000
The stage

145
00:09:58,280 --> 00:10:00,240
is all set for you.

146
00:10:00,680 --> 00:10:02,000
It's time for the star
of the show to step in.

147
00:10:03,480 --> 00:10:05,120
Once she's completely crushed,

148
00:10:05,760 --> 00:10:06,800
comfort her properly.

149
00:10:06,960 --> 00:10:08,000
Perfect chance to get closer to her.

150
00:10:09,760 --> 00:10:10,480
You actually replaced

151
00:10:10,480 --> 00:10:12,200
your father's "Love That Remains"?

152
00:10:12,200 --> 00:10:14,080
A lot of people came here
just for that piece.

153
00:10:14,080 --> 00:10:15,560
Why didn't you discuss
this with me first?

154
00:10:15,560 --> 00:10:16,320
Discuss it?

155
00:10:16,720 --> 00:10:17,520
With you?

156
00:10:21,280 --> 00:10:21,960
Mr. Qiao,

157
00:10:22,440 --> 00:10:23,840
if you don't trust me,

158
00:10:23,840 --> 00:10:25,120
then why bring me in to help?

159
00:10:26,400 --> 00:10:27,920
Just a reminder. Don't get too
caught up in your act.

160
00:10:29,920 --> 00:10:31,200
You'd better not do anything reckless.

161
00:10:31,680 --> 00:10:33,160
If something goes wrong,

162
00:10:33,160 --> 00:10:34,320
it'll be too late for regrets.

163
00:11:08,799 --> 00:11:10,869
♪We say good morning, we say good night♪

164
00:11:10,869 --> 00:11:14,289
♪We say we miss each other,
but never speak of the hurt♪

165
00:11:15,889 --> 00:11:17,779
♪The sweeter it is, the luckier we seem♪

166
00:11:17,779 --> 00:11:21,769
♪Yet the more romantic,
the rougher the road♪

167
00:11:23,009 --> 00:11:24,869
♪Let me go, set me free♪

168
00:11:24,869 --> 00:11:28,909
♪Let me drown in reckless silence♪

169
00:11:29,449 --> 00:11:34,859
♪We were perfect for each other,
yet you never admitted it♪

170
00:11:36,209 --> 00:11:38,349
♪The freedom you gave me♪

171
00:11:38,349 --> 00:11:41,989
♪Became the heaviest chain I bear♪

172
00:11:43,249 --> 00:11:45,519
♪Love can barely move forward♪

173
00:11:45,519 --> 00:11:49,299
♪Yet the words still linger unspoken♪

174
00:11:50,399 --> 00:11:52,639
♪The closeness I long for♪

175
00:11:52,639 --> 00:11:57,029
♪There's no need for you
to keep avoiding it♪

176
00:11:57,439 --> 00:11:59,259
♪I don't want to break free♪

177
00:11:59,259 --> 00:12:04,629
♪Take back the chains
disguised as freedom♪
